{"tid":692420,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"「時間管理」點善用工餘時間增加生產力？","createTime":"2018-06-06T15:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T05:35:54.000Z","uid":179648,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d0f7d7a28f98a75eb9eb069567f6dcf7cbc077dd","tid":692420,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:46:05.000Z","msg":"返放工坐車，放工後，星期六日，呢到加加埋埋其實都唔少時間。不過總係不知不覺就hea咗過去。<br />\n<br />\n見到啲前輩返正職都兼顧到行山做運動，副業或者進修學語言，真係寫個服字。其實有咩方法分配到之餘，仲要意志保持到？"},{"pid":"e09aa3aa4c4454a89d9e56672d878e04cc51c88d","tid":692420,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:48:42.000Z","msg":"保持意志 真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c72e4f92c050933a1126d369e25e65af595b65","tid":692420,"uid":123308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:52:38.000Z","msg":"GTD"},{"pid":"11699aa2ecbd5ce100befe80d48f608bcbfef3d0","tid":692420,"uid":179648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T16:16:02.000Z","msg":"返放工我試過聽電台，聽下新聞咁，但坐地鐵收得唔穩定，聽聽下就無心機。"},{"pid":"98bcce6334ab8ba55b313077ebaabea084f69fe6","tid":692420,"uid":69013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52c72e4f92c050933a1126d369e25e65af595b65","tid":692420,"uid":123308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:52:38.000Z","msg":"GTD"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T18:25:48.000Z","msg":"我堅持左3個月，上星期開始無寫，見到又想寫返，thanks 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca5bcb752dd7767341d468e8b906bba52b78b40","tid":692420,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98bcce6334ab8ba55b313077ebaabea084f69fe6","tid":692420,"uid":69013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52c72e4f92c050933a1126d369e25e65af595b65","tid":692420,"uid":123308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:52:38.000Z","msg":"GTD"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T18:25:48.000Z","m