既我就無寫到，後來買返就繼續了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我係用0.38 可擦既原子筆。"},{"pid":"8a094409448133920ab7ed30d4f6ff00ded5a62c","tid":692420,"uid":69037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:17:21.000Z","msg":"MOCC"},{"pid":"e445bc5900fa9a8e8fdab88318239ac9d19737c1","tid":692420,"uid":69037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a094409448133920ab7ed30d4f6ff00ded5a62c","tid":692420,"uid":69037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:17:21.000Z","msg":"MOCC"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:19:25.000Z","msg":"MOOC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nedx coursera"},{"pid":"f33e25ca3be1cc2d4dadcb42a41d476b1b74b63e","tid":692420,"uid":838,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:20:03.000Z","msg":"令自己無「工餘時間」就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09cd83dad7d384ca95664783cb1ac44c1ec62c1e","tid":692420,"uid":179648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f33e25ca3be1cc2d4dadcb42a41d476b1b74b63e","tid":692420,"uid":838,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T02:20:03.000Z","msg":"令自己無「工餘時間」就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:56:02.000Z","msg":"瘋狂返工炒散咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0119dbf5e0067e3e2c3b43bfede9ae9745d798","tid":692420,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T16:26:12.000Z","msg":"搭單問吓有冇巴打用時間管理 app <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nso far 試過 aTimeLogger 2、BlockyTime，不過仲觀望緊其他"},{"pid":"81e750013fac9a572cc86de839532467367a56f3","tid":692420,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T16:27:28.000Z","msg":"放工都好拿累<br />\n有冇咩方法keep精力？"},{"pid":"735306ce478ea98819baee419377b8746fd6f785","tid":692420,"u